JADX decompiles DEX bytecode to readable Java source
apkleaks automates secret detection with pattern matching
Python automation enables scalable security assessments
Comprehensive analysis requires multiple complementary tools
Continue practicing with different APK files to refine your analysis skills and expand your understanding of Android security vulnerabilities.
